NHS Area Team geographies for England

Source: R/data.R
at_sp_df.Rd

A dataframe containing the geographies for NHS Area Teams.

at_sp_df

Format

A data frame with ~87.5k observations and 12 columns:

long

Longitude

lat

Lattitude

group

Group id for polygons

id

Numeric id for Area Team, 0-9

NHSATCD

ONS code for Area Team

NHSATNM

Area Team name

OBJECTID

Id for an object. Only used for plotting

hole

Logical value for whether geography is a hole. Only used for plotting

piece

Only used for plotting

order

Gives plotting order

Shape_STAr

Only used for plotting

Shape_STLe

Only used for plotting

Source

Office for National Statistics
